article.headline: Young's 20 lead Southern Utah over UT Rio Grande Valley 79-59
article.description: — Zion Young scored 20 points as Southern Utah beat UT Rio Grande Valley 79-59 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Young's 20 lead Southern Utah over UT Rio Grande Valley 79-59
article.story: CEDAR CITY, Utah -- — Zion Young scored 20 points as Southern Utah beat UT Rio Grande Valley 79-59 on Saturday night. Young was 6-of-14 shooting, including 3 for 9 from 3-point range, and went 5 for 7 from the line for the Thunderbirds (9-13, 4-7 Western Athletic Conference). Parsa Fallah scored 17 points and added five rebounds. Elijah Elliott finished with 18 points for the Vaqueros (6-16, 2-9). Daylen Williams added 11 points and six rebounds for UT Rio Grande Valley. Isaiah Barganier also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
